		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#087d9a" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#087d9a">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1183" width="439" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">安德留斯抬起身子放出3道风刃，各造成<span color="#7fffd7">41.6%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1631" width="425" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">安德留斯仰起头朝空中咆哮，在全场产生持续性风暴，造成<span color="#7fffd7">0.416%</span><span>至</span><span color="#7fffd7">8.716%</span><span>伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span>，离安德留斯越远伤害越高(</span><span color="#7fffd7">0.166%x距离+0.416%</span><span>)。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/安德留斯.assets/Image_17.png')" x="720" y="1098">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/安德留斯.assets/Image_18.png')" x="1391" y="1545">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">安德留斯使用左或右爪迅速划击，造成<span color="#99ffff">58.3%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="447" width="423" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">安德留斯在落地的位置产生寒气，随后跳跃至此，造成<span color="#99ffff">83.3%</span><span>伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span>，并产生一个</span><span color="#99ffff">冰元素晶球</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="671" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">安德留斯突然朝前方进行一次疾冲，造成<span color="#99ffff">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="671" width="423" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">安德留斯在原地晃动全身，凝聚空气中的水汽，不断产生冰锥下坠，造成<span color="#99ffff">25%</span><span>伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span>，持续30s。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1183" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">处在安德留斯身后时，安德留斯甩动尾部，造成<span color="#99ffff">58.3%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1631" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">生命值低于<span color="#ffcebf">15%</span><span>或耗时太久时，安德留斯在玩家附近不断召唤小狼幻影攻击玩家，造成</span><span color="#99ffff">25%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1407" width="408" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">安德留斯抬起身子在途经上产生霜面，走在霜面上减速<span color="#ffcdbf">30%</span><span>，并附着冰元素，随后霜面开始起爆，造成</span><span color="#99ffff">41.6%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="895" width="436" height="172" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">二阶段时，6个<span textDecoration="underline">寒石柱</span><span>出现在场地边缘，若其被安德留斯的</span><span color="#99ffcc">风元素技能</span><span>命中则会延时5s后爆炸，造成</span><span color="#99ffff">66.6%</span><span>伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span>，并产生1-5个</span><span color="#99ffff">冰元素晶球</span><span>；寒石周围的冰霜持续造成</span><span color="#99ffff">4.16%</span><span>伤害并减速</span><span color="#ffcdbf">12%</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="433" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">安德留斯在自身位置产生霜气，随后旋转身迅速划击，造成<span color="#99ffff">83.3%</span><span>伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span>，并产生一个</span><span color="#99ffff">冰元素晶球</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="447" width="439" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">安德留斯甩尾，扔出5个冰锥，命中造成<span color="#99ffff">25%</span><span>伤害，同时在命中点产生一个冰簇，片刻后爆炸造成</span><span color="#99ffff">58.3%</span><span>伤害，留下一个</span><span color="#99ffff">冰元素晶球</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
