		<RichText x="738" y="895" width="438" height="172" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">低于<span color="#ffbfbf">55%生命值</span><span>或拖太长时间，安德留斯绕场地边缘跑动，跑3圈，前两圈跑完3/4圈直接冲撞，最后一圈跑完起跳下落。被场地边缘跑动的安德留斯撞到造成</span><span color="#99ffff">100%</span><span>伤害，周围的冰霜地面持续造成</span><span color="#99ffff">16.6%</span><span>伤害，且减速</span><span color="#ffcdbf">12%</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/安德留斯.assets/Image_30.png')" x="719" y="809">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1407" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">安德留斯使用左或右爪迅速划击，造成<span color="#7fffd7">58.3%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/安德留斯.assets/Image_31.png')" x="1391" y="1321">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="66" y="1296" width="442" height="39" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">寒石柱：<span color="#99ffff">4冻</span><span>盾，可破坏，但是可再生，受安德留斯风元素技能攻击会进入5s的引信时间，随后爆炸，并清除附近的冰地面。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
